 The First Years® by Learning Curve Deluxe Double miPump

We all want whats best for our baby, and when it comes to nutrition, doctors agree that breastmilk provides the finest nourishment that nature has to offer.  And its great for moms too, since breastfeeding supplies wonderful postpartum benefits.

But with our busy schedules, we cant always be available to breastfeed.  Thats where miPump comes in.  This innovative breast pump by The First Years was designed after gaining extensive input from lactation experts, and securing the feedback of moms to better understand their breastfeeding needs.

Through this research, the First Years recognized the need for a pump thats comfortable, simple, quiet, and affordable.  MiPump meets these needs and more.

MiPumps sleek, practical design makes it easy to use.  Its simple to clean and assemble.  And only a few, short steps are needed before its ready for use.

The soft, flexi-fit breast shield molds to fit you properly and securely keeping you comfortable as you pump.  The multilevel controls allow you to adjust miPumps suction level, and the convenient LED display gives you a visual cue to your suction level.

As youll discover, comfort is one of the most important aspects of pumping.  The more comfortable you are, the more successful youll be at expressing milk for your baby.

MiPump is so quiet only you will know youre pumping.  But dont let its discrete nature fool you.  MiPump does not sacrifice motor strength.  Its professional grade performance efficiently expresses your milk without any loud humming.

MiPump is so compact and lightweight, its a cinch to take with you.  When youre on the go, just place MiPump in the stylish bag that it comes with, and MiPump offers electric or battery operation to give you complete freedom when away from home.

All growing families are looking to spend money wisely, and using miPump allows this to happen.  Not only is miPump a great value on its own, but it also allows families to save money by making it unnecessary to buy formula.  And if moms follow the American Academy of Pediatrics recommendation of giving breastmilk to their baby for one year, the health benefits for their baby and financial benefit for their family are significant.

MiPump by The First Years: designed to balance whats healthiest for your precious baby with the busy schedules and comfort needs of moms.
